modules.description: This module implements an MQTT client for connecting to an MQTT broker, publishing messages to topics, and subscribing to topics with specified quality of service (QoS) levels. It supports operations like connecting with optional TLS and authentication, publishing messages with configurable QoS and retention, and handling incoming messages asynchronously. Concrete use cases include IoT device communication, real-time telemetry ingestion, and event-driven microservices messaging.
